        <section class="container my-5" dir="rtl">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-center">שאלות ותשובות – INOKIM CYBORG</h2>
            <div class="accordion" id="cyborgFaq">
          
              <div class="accordion-item text-end">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
                  <button class="accordion-button text-end" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="answer1">
                    מה מגיע בערכה?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="answer1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#cyborgFaq">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    צג<br>
                     ידית גז<br>
                     כפתור הדלקה<br>
                     רמקול
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
              <div class="accordion-item text-end">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-end" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer2">
                    האם הערכה עמידה במים?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="answer2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#cyborgFaq">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                     כן, הערכה עמידה בגשם.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
              <div class="accordion-item text-end">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-end" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer3">
                    האם המערכת מותאמת לכל דגמי OX?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="answer3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#cyborgFaq">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                     כן, היא מתאימה לכל דגמי OX משנת 2018 ואילך.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
              <div class="accordion-item text-end">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed text-end" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer4">
                    האם המערכת עובדת עם בקרים ששודרגו בעבר?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="answer4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#cyborgFaq">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                     רק על בקרי אינוקים וגאגר.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
